name.zh_CN: Tabby：基于人工智能的文本补全

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tabby uses AI to help you complete text input quickly and efficiently.
short.zh_CN: Tabby 利用人工智能技术为您提供文本补全建议，让您快速高效地完成文本输入。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tabby is a Chrome extension that uses AI to help you complete text input quickly and efficiently. It does this by providing suggestions for the next word or phrase you should type based on the context of the text you have already typed.
